EN: My sister trusts me a lot.

ZH: 他们之间有一种无话不谈的信任。
EN: There is a trust between them where they can talk about anything.

ZH: 这本书对传统文化的描述很有信度。
EN: This book has a lot of credibility in describing traditional culture.

